translation.Name: Greece Note Doubts
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_0: Does High Command not understand what we are fighting? The whole Keres zone is just a pot waiting to boil over! Every time I have to return the size of the horde is even larger.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_1: Those fences will not stand, and we definitely don't have enough bullets to keep up. Day and night from over here I can hear the constant gunfire. It never seems to stop...
